params._collateralAmount: pass the amount of EGold token as a collateral to be deposited in Lending Pool.

returns._0: borrowEinrAmt calculated loan amount based on the collateral deposited.

params._amount: pass the amount of EINR token to be borrowed or deposited.

returns._0: bool whether the KYC is true or false for the particular User account.

params._EINRamount: pass the amount of EINR token to deposit in Lending Pool.

getAmountWithInterest().details: This function calculate the interest earn by the depositor.

returns._0: withdrawAmount is the amount with interest earn by depositor.

getBalanceOfLPtoken(address).details: In this function get User balance of LP token minted.

returns._0: lptokenbal gives User balance of LP token minted in Lending pool.

getBorrowEINRAmount(address).details: In this function get User balance of EINR token Borrowed from Lending Pool.

returns._0: baleinborrow gives User balance of EINR token borrowed from Lending pool.

getOwnerDepositEINRBalance(address).details: In this function get User balance of EINR token Deposited in Lending Pool.

returns._0: baleinr gives User balance of EINR token stored in Lending pool.

getTotalOfSupplyEINRPool().details: In this function get the Total Supply of EINR in Lending Pool.

returns._0: totalSupply gives total amount of EINR stored in Lending .

getUserRepayAmount(address).details: In this function get User balance of EINR token to be repaid in Lending Pool.

returns._0: repaybal gives User repay amount of EINR token with interest borrowed.

getborrowerRepayAmount().details: This function calculate the interest to be repaid by the borrower.

returns._0: repayAmount is the amount with interest to repay by the borrower.

repayEINRLoan(uint256).details: In this function the User can repay their EINR asset in Lending Pool.

params.finalRepayAmount: repay the amount of EINR token with Interest in Lending Pool.
